---
import SectionHeader from "./SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="section-pad border-y border-[var(--line)] bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.36)]">
  <div class="site-shell">
    <SectionHeader
      eyebrow="About"
      title="I work closest to the messy middle: product ambition, backend reality, and AI behavior."
    />

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr]">
      <p class="body-copy text-lg">
        My strongest work sits where a product needs more than a polished interface: dependable APIs, cloud primitives, data movement, operational visibility, and AI workflows that behave predictably enough to ship.
      </p>
      <p class="body-copy text-lg">
        I have built edtech platforms, compliance and identity systems, emissions analytics, launch-scale onboarding flows, and AI-driven finance products. The common thread is pragmatic architecture: small enough to move, strong enough to scale.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
